==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Starlight
<hw>Star"light`</hw> <pr>(-l⟦imac⟧t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The light
given by the stars.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nor walk by moon,⟦br⟧
Or glittering <qex>starlight</qex>, without thee is sweet.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Starlight</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Starlight
<hw>Star"light`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Lighted by the stars, or by the
stars only; <as>as, a <ex>starlight</ex> night</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>starlight</qex> evening and a morning fair.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Starlike</ent>⟦br⟧
